      "category": "regulatory",
      "severity": "high",
      "evidence": "estimate capital expenditures of approximately $875 million through 2026 to meet emission reduction targets"
    },
    {
      "factor": "Increasing physical climate risks from extreme weather events causing operational disruptions and production losses",
      "category": "environmental",
      "severity": "high",
      "evidence": "Hurricane Delphine caused significant damage to our Gulf Coast refining facilities, resulting in production losses of approximately $340 million"
    },
    {
